metadata.name: Block #1
metadata.description:
How would its eyes look if artificial intelligence were made of flesh and blood? 

Each eye has its own texture, the same goes for artificial intelligence. Is what we have created watching us? 

Will human disobedience to god be between artificial intelligence and humans? All of this is a matter of curiosity, and in this collection, 

I asked one of the most advanced artificial intelligence to draw an eye for itself. The resulting eyes were loaded onto televisions, and a work of art emerged with a "90s perspective".
